hareholders of the Company in the ratio of two equity shares for every one equity share held on 26th May,2015. As on 26th May,2015 equity shares 632,02,558 were outstanding. The bonus equity shares were issued by capitalisation of the reserves lying to the credit of the securities premium account of the Company.

7). Long Term Debt equity ratio = Long term borrowing / Total shareholder fund

8). Debt equity ratio = Total borrowing / Total shareholder fund

